Dialogue: 10,0:03:04.01,0:03:06.57,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Thế nên Mio-chan mới làm ca sĩ chính...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:06.57,0:03:09.86,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hôm ấy Mio-chan hát hay lắm cơ!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.39,0:04:02.99,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Giai điệu Sô-cô-la.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.08,0:08:20.54,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Dễ thương mà phải không?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:46.14,0:09:48.78,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Không, xin hãy nhận tấm lòng của chúng tôi..
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.07,0:10:19.65,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{\}{\an8}Không chịu! Tớ không muốn!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.65,0:10:22.36,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{\}{\an8}Coi nào, đi thôi!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.36,0:10:24.22,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{\}{\an8}Ê! Nguy hiểm—
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.87,0:13:42.16,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Này—
Dialogue: 10,0:14:17.98,0:14:23.41,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Hôm nay tớ có trà ngon lắm, nhé?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.88,0:16:11.93,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Mình làm gì thế này?
